# ── Remote dev (phone QA via Tailscale) ────────────────────────────────
# Zero config required. The Mac's Docker port bindings are reachable from
# any tailnet device at http://<mac-hostname>.<tailnet>.ts.net:3013 — just
# install Tailscale on the Mac and phone. See README → "Remote Dev" for
# the full story and the iOS DNS gotcha.

# ── Local dev port mappings (optional overrides) ───────────────────────
# DEV_PORT=3013
# RAILS_DEV_PORT=3014
